title: Learn to Paint: Getting Started With Warhammer 40,000 Magazine
description:
Follow this simple step by step tutorial, using the contents of the Getting Started with Warhammer 40,000 and the Warhammer 40,000 Paints + Tools set, to get your miniatures looking awesome in no time at all!   
     
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
